  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1062">
<l>irantu muyirvāḻtal vēṇṭiṟ parantu </l>
<l>keṭuka vulakiyaṟṟi yāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the Creator of the world has decreed even begging as a means of livelihood, may he too go abegging and perish.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
